{"type": "article", "id": 5415, "title": "鞋匠椅子", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-21T07:27:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052338471XSzGf8URqOEr9Zt.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自西班牙的设计师 Martín Azúa 带来了一款由皮革制成，并具有鞋带的产品，相信很多人的第一反应会是这是一双鞋子，但事实上它是一把椅子，设计师还给它取了个独特的名字——鞋匠椅子，其用意在于希望使用者能够像对待自己的鞋子一般，经常护理这把椅子，亦希望人们的所用之物都能带有自己的特征。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233845f9OKBgu3pyM5oEWw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052338468LJ0udbIoqYMtQ1g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233846AurWLlDszbqka6YJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233846nRtfgyU6EFi2kdMI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}